Class DroneSystem.UnitConversion

java.lang.Object
com.otabi.jcodroneedu.DroneSystem.UnitConversion
Enclosing class:
DroneSystem
public static class DroneSystem.UnitConversion extends Object
Unit conversion constants for distance measurements. Provides standard conversion factors between metric and imperial units.
